{"title":"“世界大枷庭”","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“世界大枷庭”\t池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名曰“天下一家”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实为一家天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来者不拒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拒者硬拉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欧、美、澳、拉、非、亚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俱由他独霸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“东亚共荣圈”规模比它小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“欧洲新秩序”气魄没它大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偌大的家业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何其伟也。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是家长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是家奴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你守家规，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他定家法。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独立休再提起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主权任他践踏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要自由，目无尊长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲平等，不分上下；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想和平，得跪着活；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹革命，小心脑瓜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此“大枷庭”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收起来吧！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}